General.Name: Everyday Network
General.Description: Everyday Network Co.,Ltd. operates as an Internet service providers in China. It provides network marketing services in the field of real estate properties through house365.com. The company also offers Internet microfinance; and operates a platform to provide buying, selling, financing, and renting houses. Everyday Network Co.,Ltd. was founded in 2006 and is based in Nanjing, China.
